query:
INSERT INTO user_marketing_consents (user_id, course_id, course_language_group_id, consent, email_subscription_in_mailchimp)
      VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
      ON CONFLICT (user_id, course_language_group_id)
      DO UPDATE
      SET
        course_id = $2,
        consent = $4,
        email_subscription_in_mailchimp = $5
      RETURNING id
